%section#navigate.py-5
  %h5.text-muted.mb-3 Explore
  %h2.fw-bold.mb-4 How to Navigate the AEDG

  .row.text-start
    .col-md-4.mb-4
      .circle-icon.mb-4
        %i.bi.bi-grid-3x3-gap.fs-4
      %h5.fw-bold Step 1: Access the Data Apps
      %p.text-muted.mb-2
        Visit the Data Explorer or Community Explorer to get started.

      .d-flex.flex-column.gap-2.mt-3
        = link_to 'Data Explorer →', metadata_path, class: 'btn btn-aedg-primary btn-sm'
        = link_to 'Community Explorer →', communities_path, class: 'btn btn-aedg-primary btn-sm'

    .col-md-4.mb-4        
      .circle-icon.mb-4
        %i.bi.bi-search.fs-4
      %h5.fw-bold Step 2: Search for Relevant Data
      %p.text-muted
        In the Data Explorer, use search and filters to find datasets of interest.
      %p.text-muted
        In Community Explorer, browse "On This Page" or scroll to view key energy and socioeconomic data for each community.

    .col-md-4.mb-4
      .circle-icon.mb-4
        %i.bi.bi-download.fs-4
      %h5.fw-bold Step 3: Download and Analyze Data
      %p.text-muted
        Download datasets and metadata directly to your device for further analysis and research.